HEADWORD: Affrap
<hw>Af*frap"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[Cf. It.
<ets>affrappare</ets>, <ets>frappare</ets>, to cut, mince, F.
<ets>frapper</ets> to strike. See <er>Frap</er>.]</ety> <def>To strike,
or strike down.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
